c: 33
v: 5
t: "Mubalaanje ameera kabu khubasamwana, obo nibo obuleng’aafu khu Nyasaye, ne nimulamanyile Basamwana tawe ni Abana benyu nende abetsa benyu mudini. Ne shinobutulanikhwinywe khukamwitsukhanile tawe, halali ni obutulani khukalia akemioyo chienyu chikholele katong’ane. Ne Nyasaye ni Omulesheli muno Owetsimbabaasi po"